## 🎨 Visual Database ERD (Entity Relationships)

```mermaid
erDiagram
    USER ||--o{ EMERGENCY_ALERT : "reports"
    USER ||--o{ ENDORSEMENT : "requests"
    USER ||--o{ CHAT_MESSAGE : "sends"
    USER }|--|| BARANGAY_ZONE : "assigned_to"
    
    EMERGENCY_ALERT ||--o{ ALERT_NOTIFICATION : "triggers"
    EMERGENCY_ALERT ||--o| ENDORSEMENT : "linked_to"
    
    ENDORSEMENT ||--o{ ENDORSEMENT_STATUS_LOG : "has_history"
    
    USER {
        string uid PK
        string username
        string role
        boolean isEmailBound
    }
    
    EMERGENCY_ALERT {
        int id PK
        string userId FK
        string category
        long timestamp
    }
    
    ENDORSEMENT {
        int id PK
        int alertId FK
        string username FK
        string patientName
        string status
        string caseRef
    }
```

