## 🔗 Relational Mapping (Table Connections)

The following table lists the specific columns that "connect" (Foreign Keys) different parts of the InstaCare ecosystem:

| Source Table | Source Column | Target Table | Connection Type |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `User` | `uid` | `EmergencyAlert` | **(1:N)** - Tracks which user reported an incident. |
| `User` | `username` | `Endorsement` | **(1:N)** - Links medical requests to a profile. |
| `User` | `uid` | `ActivityLog` | **(1:N)** - Audit trail for user actions. |
| `EmergencyAlert`| `id` | `Endorsement` | **(1:1)** - Connects a medical request to its source SOS. |
| `EmergencyAlert`| `id` | `AlertNotification`| **(1:N)** - Links specific alerts to SOS incidents. |
| `Endorsement` | `id` | `EndorsementStatusLog`| **(1:N)** - History of status changes (Pending -> Approved). |
| `BarangayZone` | `barName` | `User` | **(1:N)** - Assigns users to their specific local zone. |
| `User` | `uid` | `ChatMessage` | **(1:N)** - Identifies sender/receiver in chats. |

---

## 📊 Database Architecture (Complete Table Registry)

| Table Name | Primary Purpose | Key Fields |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `User` | Resident Identity & Role Auth | `uid`, `email`, `role`, `isEmailBound`, `fullName` |
| `EmergencyAlert` | Real-time Incident Reports | `id`, `userId`, `category`, `label`, `timestamp`, `status` |
| `Endorsement` | Med-Cert & Assistance Requests | `id`, `alertId`, `username`, `patientName`, `purpose`, `status` |
| `Hospital` | Dynamically Fetched Medical Facilities | `id`, `name`, `latitude`, `longitude`, `phone`, `capacity` |
| `EvacuationCenter` | Disaster Shelters & Assembly Points | `id`, `name`, `status`, `source`, `centerType`, `latitude` |
| `AssistantMessage` | Cara AI Conversion Memory | `msgId`, `content`, `isBot`, `timestamp` |
| `ChatMessage` | Responder-to-User Communication | `id`, `senderId`, `receiverId`, `message`, `type` |
| `Notification` | System & Local Alerts | `id`, `title`, `body`, `type`, `isRead`, `timestamp` |
| `BarangayZone` | Administrative Boundary Data | `barName`, `zoneCoords`, `pincode` |
| `EndorsementStatusLog` | Audit Trail for Med-Cert Requests | `id`, `endorsementId`, `status`, `remarks`, `timestamp` |
| `AlertNotification` | Specific Notifications tied to SOS | `id`, `alertId`, `title`, `message` |
| `ActivityLog` | General System Audit Trail | `id`, `userId`, `description`, `type`, `time` |
| `EmergencyContact` | User's Personal Trusted Contacts | `id`, `userId`, `contactName`, `phoneNumber` |
| `Guide` | First Aid Educational Content | `id`, `title`, `category`, `difficulty`, `videoUrl` |
| `DisasterGuide` | Natural Disaster Survival Content | `id`, `title`, `disasterType`, `stepsJson` |

---

> [!TIP]
> **Technical Note on UI Sync:** The `EditProfileBottomSheet` uses direct **SessionManager-to-AppDatabase** synchronization, ensuring that email verification status and theme preferences are updated across all dashboard fragments instantly.
